\begin_layout Standard
部分子模型的另一个结果是
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
W_{1}(x,Q)=\frac{Q^{2}}{4x^{2}}W_{2}(x,Q),\text{ for }Q\gg m_{p}
\]

\end_inset

