，也就是说，我们需要
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\mathcal{M}(\gamma^{*}p^{+}\to X)=e\epsilon^{\mu}\bra{X}J_{\mu}(0)\ket{P}\label{eq:32.75}
